WolfBlade::

She ran through the trees in wolf form. She was running towards the a 
scent that was ever so faint on the breeze. It was the smell of 
battle It caused her mech fluids rising faster through her spark.  
She felt the very fur on the back of her neck stand up on end.  She 
wanted to hurry before it was to late. She raced to the Maximal 
stronghold in hopes of making it there on time.  "BLAST! I hope I get 
there in time."  She moved as fast as her legs would go in order to 
help with the war.
